    <h1>Global Warming</h1>
    <p>Global warming is the increase in Earth's average temperature due to greenhouse gases.</p>
    
    <h2>Causes</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Burning of fossil fuels</li>
        <li>Deforestation</li>
        <li>Industrial pollution</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Effects</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Rising sea levels</li>
        <li>Extreme weather</li>
        <li>Melting glaciers</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Solutions</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Plant more trees</li>
        <li>Use renewable energy</li>
        <li>Save electricity</li>
        <li>For more information go to below website :</li>
        <li><a href = "https://www.britannica.com/science/global-warming">google</a></li>
